data.name: rtbChangelog.Text
data.value:
Version 0.3.2 (28.09.2022) + Added support for 'random amount of same/different items' to duplicate finder
Version 0.3.1 (10.09.2022) + Added support for 'random amount of same/different items' to main window + Added option to reset entire software
Version 0.3.0 (17.07.2022) + Added Settings + Added Datapack Profiles + Added Schemes * Changed default view in main menu * Fixed several occations where the software was only called "Random Item Giver"
Version 0.2.3 (10.06.2022) + Added progress bar to duplicate finder and when adding items + Added fast item adding method * Fixed software freezing on duplicate finder and when adding items * Improved performance and speed for several actions * You can no longer edit settings while adding items * Output is now resizable
Version 0.2.2 (07.06.2022) * Fixed critical lag spike issue * Change version selector * Remove warnings when adding items to 1.19 or 1.17 datapack * Fixed issue when adding duplicate to datapack
Version 0.2.1 (14.05.2022) + Added support for goat horn loot table (1.19+) * Slightly changed application icon * Fixed a typo in the Item List Importer
Version 0.2.0 (10.05.2022) + Added output log + Added feature to import item lists from text file + Added feature to add a list of items + Added option to open datapack folder in the menu * Its now possible to select wether all items should use the same prefix or you want to give each item its own prefix manually * Improved duplicate detection when adding items * Improved design of changelog * Duplicate finder now also shows amount of total duplicates * Fixed exception when datapack path was invalid * Fixed several typos
Version 0.1.5 (16.04.2022) + Added support for 1.17 to the duplicate finder * Improved several messages in the duplicate finder * Improved message that shows up when a feature is not available yet * The items in the duplicate finder list now no longer have quotation marks
Version 0.1.4 (11.04.2022) + Added link to GitHub page in 'about' menu + Added Duplicate finder
Version 0.1.3 (05.04.2022) + Added automatic datapack detection + Added error message when trying to add an item, that already exists in datapacks + Added tools in the menu bar * Slightly improved performance by cleaning up the code
Version 0.1.2 (19.03.2022) + Added 1.19 support + Added 1.16 support
Version 0.1.1 (14.03.2022) * Fixed a bug which caused items to not be added to the correct loot tables * Fixed a bug where the application would crash if no text was entered in the ID textbox * Windows now start at the center of the screen * Slightly resorted the checkboxes in main window
Version 0.1.0 (12.03.2022) + Added changelog + Added license in 'about' window * Fixed typo in startup message
Version 0.0.1 (05.03.2022) * Initial pre-release
